david j lesar  wikipedia david j lesar from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search david j lesar born david john lesar may   madison wisconsin us residence houston texas us alma mater university of wisconsin–madison bsmba occupation businessman  chairman at halliburton  salary us   total us   predecessor dick cheney david john lesar is an american businessman who is the chairman of halliburton energy services he was the ceo of halliburton for  years from  to  trained as a certified public accountant lesar spent  years at arthur andersen he had spent most of his career at andersen where he worked on their halliburton account in  lesar was hired by halliburton as a new vice president contents  education  career  controversies  references educationedit lesar was born in madison wisconsin and is a  graduate of the university of wisconsin–madison where he earned both a bachelor of science and a master of business administration degree careeredit as a certified public accountant lesar spent  years working at arthur andersen in  lesar joined halliburton within a year of his arrival lesar was appointed as ceo of kbr in addition to his duties as cfo of halliburton in  lesar was appointed as the companys president and chief operating officer in  lesar became ceo of halliburton he stepped down as the ceo in  and is now the chairman of halliburtons board of directors he also serves on the board of directors at lyondell chemical is a member of the upstream committee of the american petroleum institute and is on the board of directors of the american iranian council an organization devoted to the normalization of americaniranian relations controversiesedit the movie iraq for sale the war profiteers claims that lesar has been paid over  by halliburton since the beginning of iraq war but this amount has risen significantly since the release of the film according to the wall street journal lesar received about  million in  alone not including stock options or other deferred incentives  a  increase over his  pay package according to a securities filing in november  lesar faced criticism over his bid to take over baker hughes inc  the smaller oilfield services rival in an email to mr lesar described halliburton’s actions as intransigent and inappropriate referencesedit  the leases and related families beth lease brynildson  p   reuters officers  directors detail halliburton co new york stock exchange  american iranian council leadership  halliburton ceo dave lesar knows controversy wsj nov   v t e petroleum industry petroleum primary energy benchmarks argus sour bonny light brent dubai indonesian isthmus light japan cocktail opec reference basket tapis urals western canadian select west texas intermediate data natural gas consumption production reserves imports exports price petroleum consumption production reserves imports exports price of gasoline and diesel exploration core sampling geophysics integrated asset modelling petroleum engineering reservoir simulation seismic to simulation petroleum geology petrophysics reflection seismology seismic inversion seismic source drilling blowout completion squeeze job differential sticking directional drilling geosteering drilling engineering drilling fluid invasion drill stem test lost circulation measurement tracers underbalanced drilling well logging production petroleum fiscal regime concessions production sharing agreements artificial lift pumpjack submersible pump esp gas lift downstream enhanced oil recovery eor steam injection gas reinjection midstream petroleum product pipeline transport refining upstream water injection well intervention xt history  oil embargo  oil crisis  energy crisis s oil glut  oil price shock s energy crisis s oil glut founders history of the petroleum industry nationalization opec gecf seven sisters standard oil oil market timelines provinces and fields list of natural gas fields list of oil fields east midlands oil province east texas gulf of mexico 